Package: TopSA
Type: Package
Title: Estimate Sensitivity Indices using the Topological Homology
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2018-09-26
Authors@R: c(person("Maikol", "Solís", email = "maikol.solis@ucr.ac.cr", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Alberto", "Hernández", email = "albertojose.hernandez@ucr.ac.cr", role = c("ctb")), person("Ronald A.", "Zuñiga-Rojas", email = "ronald.zunigarojas@ucr.ac.cr", role = c("ctb")))
Author: Maikol Solís [aut, cre]
        Alberto Hernandez [ctb]
        Ronald A. Zuñiga-Rojas [ctb]
Maintainer: Maikol Solís <maikol.solis@ucr.ac.cr>
Description: Estimate sensitivity indices reconstructing the embedding manifold of the data. The reconstruction is done via a Vietoris Rips with a fixed radius. Then the homology of order 2 and the indices are estimated. 
